<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>이미지 게시판 - 글쓰기</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --naver-green: #03c75a;
      --line: #e5e7eb;
      --bg: #f5f7fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Malgun Gothic", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 22px auto;
      padding: 0 14px;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .guide {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    button, a {
      margin-top: 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0f172a;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .primary {
      border-color: var(--naver-green);
      background: var(--naver-green);
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="card">
      <h2>이미지 게시판 글쓰기</h2>
      <form action="/image-boards/write" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목" required />
        <textarea name="content" rows="6" placeholder="내용" required></textarea>
        <input type="file" name="imageFile" accept="image/*" required />
        <div class="guide">20MB 이하 파일만 업로드 가능합니다.</div>
        <button class="primary" type="submit">등록</button>
      </form>
      <a href="/image-boards">목록으로</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
